      <li>GitHub repository: <code>holbertonschool-sysadmin_devops</code></li>
        <li>Directory: <code>0x0B-https_ssl</code></li>
        <li>File: <code>2-haproxy_ssl_termination</code></li>
    </ul>



  
      
